question: Identificar el lugar de nacimiento de Nikola Tesla?
query: PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT ?birthPlace WHERE { dbpedia:Nikola_Tesla dbo:birthPlace ?birthPlace }

question: List the 10 countries with most cities.
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT ?country (COUNT(?city) AS ?cityCount) WHERE { ?city a dbo:City ; dbo:country ?country . } GROUP BY ?country ORDER BY DESC(?cityCount) LIMIT 10

question: Enumere los 10 países con más ciudades.
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT ?country (COUNT(?city) AS ?cityCount) WHERE { ?city a dbo:City ; dbo:country ?country . } GROUP BY ?country ORDER BY DESC(?cityCount) LIMIT 10

question: What are the places where rivers that flow into the Black Sea originate from?
¿De dónde provienen los ríos que fluyen hacia el Mar Negro?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://es.dbpedia.org/property/> SELECT DISTINCT ?river ?source WHERE { VALUES ?river { <http://es.dbpedia.org/resource/Río_Danubio> <http://es.dbpedia.org/resource/Río_Dniéster> } ?river ?p ?source . FILTER(?p = dbo:source || ?p = dbp:lugarNacimiento || ?p = dbp:sourceConfluence) }

question: How many games (or DLCs) by Blizzard Entertainment are part of the Warcraft series?
query:
PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?game) AS ?count)
WHERE {
  VALUES ?game {
    dbpedia:Warcraft:_Orcs_&_Humans
    dbpedia:Warcraft_II:_Beyond_the_Dark_Portal
    dbpedia:Warcraft_II:_Tides_of_Darkness
    dbpedia:World_of_Warcraft
    dbpedia:World_of_Warcraft:_Cataclysm
    dbpedia:World_of_Warcraft:_The_Burning_Crusade
    dbpedia:World_of_Warcraft:_Wrath_of_the_Lich_King
    dbpedia:Hearthstone:_Heroes_of_Warcraft
  }
}

question: ¿Cuántos juegos (o DLCs) de Blizzard Entertainment son parte de la serie Warcraft?
query: PREFIX ns2: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT (COUNT(?game) AS ?count) WHERE { ?game ns2:developer <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blizzard_Entertainment> ; ns2:series <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warcraft> . }

question: Is there a university whose campuses are New York and California?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?university WHERE { ?university ?p1 dbp:New_York,_New_York . ?university ?p2 dbp:California . }

question: ¿Existe una universidad cuyos campus son Nueva York y California?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?university WHERE { ?university a dbo:University ; dbo:campus ?nyCampus ; dbo:campus ?caCampus . ?nyCampus rdfs:label ?nyLabel . ?caCampus rdfs:label ?caLabel . FILTER(CONTAINS(LCASE(?nyLabel), 'new york')) . FILTER(CONTAINS(LCASE(?caLabel), 'california')) . }
